===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  imap_num_recent(IMAP\Connection $imap): int~

Gets the number of recent messages in the current mailbox.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{imap}

  An IMAP\Connection instance.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

Returns the number of recent messages in the current mailbox, as an integer.

